detail.name: Son Gohan : Youth
detail.effect: [On Play] Look at 10 cards from the top of your deck, reveal up to 2 green cards with costs of 6 and add them to your hand. Place the rest at the bottom of their owner's deck in a random order.

detail.name: 孫悟飯：幼年期
detail.effect: 【登場時】自分のデッキの上から10枚を見て、緑のコスト6のカード2枚までを公開し、手札に加える。残りをランダムにデッキの下に置く。
